latestIgtvVideos.title: MY ARMS WORKOUT ROUTINE💪🏻
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
🔴WORKOUT DETAILS 👇🏻
• Barbel curl + hamme curl ( 4 sets  8/8/7/6reps)

• Incline Db curl ( 4sets 8/8/7/6 reps)

• Machine preacher curl (4 sets 10/10/8/8 reps)

• Tricep push down (4 sets 15/15/15/15 reps)

• Rope overhead ext (4 sets 12/12/10/10

• Tricep dips (4 sets 10/10/8/8 reps)

🔵Make sure you warm up your biceps and tricep before the working set .Do atleast 30-40 resp in your warm up with light weight db or with the empty bar

your will feel the crazy pump in your arm after this workout routine . add this workout routine in your schdule atleast once a week .i'm damn sure you will love this routine. 

Till then bye bye take care and enjoy your post workout drink or meal🤪 
 
#eatbigtogetbig #liftlife #staystrong
